channel.title: Due to popular demand 0.o
channel.description:
I guess I'm coming back early? WAY early, lol. You're making me feel bad for leaving :(
I keep getting messages on msn of all these people who go in 'awe' at the very sight of me o.0 they're tellin' me how there is no 'moparscape' anymore.. which I doubt is true, I wasn't that imoportant, now was I?
People tellin me the mods aren't doing their jobs, which I know isn't true - they're stretching the truth now, I know for a fact there's some great mods here.
Well, anyways to be honest I've been beatin myself up for telling some people I would do some things that I haven't been doing, which requires me being here on Moparscape.
So.. yeah, I guess I'm back. Definitely as active as before, nothing else to do.
I even feel a little dumb for announcing these things, but this is just so people can stop bothering me on msn now, I'm not trying to be mean but I get mass pms.. constantly.
